Description: The Jack Georges Voyager collection is made from hand-stained vegetable re-tanned buffalo leather that grows in character and beauty and builds a rich patina as it ages. The leather itself is full-grain and is not corrected - the untouched grain allows the fiber to keep its full strength and durability. Whether you need a soft-structured briefcase, messenger bag, cross body bag, or accessory, the Voyager collection is sure to make a statement.This slim leather messenger bag offers plenty of space and function despite its smaller size. Hand made from buffalo leather, it has extended zippered top closure for easy access to everything inside. Its roomy main compartment is fully lined and includes a padded pocket for laptops with up to 13" screens. It has room for your files, folders, and documents. Organizer pockets inside will hold your mobile phone, portable hard drive, pens, charging cords, and accessories. Dual open front pockets and zippered front & back pockets offer added storage for items that you need easy access to when you're on the go. The adjustable shoulder strap is backed with cotton webbing for strength and grip on your shoulder.
